   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Hermeros son of Haryotes and his p(artners) to Pakoibis son of Paeris son of Horos, greetings.  I have received from you . . . the 4th year of Imperator Caesar Vespasianus Augustus, Thoth 28 . . . I, Hermeros, [have signed].</ab>
